         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Melbourne Botan Garden ¶ 24/4/71 ¶ Sir, ¶  ¶ Allow me to inform you that I have just been requested by Dr Hermann Wagner the editor of the Gotha Hof-Kalender, ¶ Gothaischer Hofkalender(Almanach de Got...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">71.04.24c</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">To John Robertson</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">No. 71/3077, 1/2167 letters received, Colonial Secretary's Department, Archives Authority of New South Wales, Sydney.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; "/>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn0" n="1">
                  <p rend="FootnoteText"
                     style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>MS written<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>by<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Georg Luehmann<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>and<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>signed and addressed by M. MS annotated below the date:<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>'1 May […]'.</p>
               </note>Melbourne Botan Garden</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">24/4/71</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Sir,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Allow me to inform you that I have just been requested by Dr Hermann Wagner the editor of the Gotha Hof-Kalender,<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn1" n="2">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">Gothaischer Hofkalender</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                           <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>(</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">Almanach de Gotha</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">).</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                           <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Letter not found.</seg>
                     </p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>to obtain for him some summary of statistic data, concerning the trade, Customs, postal Service, telegraph Department, Census, railways, Volunteer force, mines, lands public expenditure and income, and any other data in reference to your Colony.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn2" n="3">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>See also M to J. Robertson, 17 March 1872 (in this edition as 72-03-17b).</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>As the Gotha Kalender is universally used in the diplomatic service, and also otherwise much consulted all over the Globe, you may be pleased perhaps to accede to Dr Wagners request, and if so forward kindly to him direct any documents bearing on the statistic information desired — or entrust such documents to me for early transmission to Gotha. I may add that the information required is only for 1870 and that the documents should be forwarded by the May Mail.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn3" n="4">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>'I may add … May Mail'<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">underlined in an unknown hand</seg>.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>MS annotated in an unknown hand, probably Robertson's: 'May<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>be permitted<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>as far as practicable. 2 May 71', and initialled on 3 May 1871. A<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>minute in response<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>follows:<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>'It has been ascertained that no part of the 1870 Statistical Register is yet in type or even compiled. [8] May',<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>to which Robertson(?) replied,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>'May be so informed, but that when in print a copy shall be forwarded to him. 9 May 71'. The file was initialled again on 11 May 1871. A final annotation in another unknown hand reads: 'Registrar General. Dr Mueller. 15. May 1871'.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Letter to M not found.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">I have the honor to be</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Sir,</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Your very obedient</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">The honorable the Chief Secretary of N. S. Wales</p>
         </div>
